title: Help!
body:
Hi. 
do i still get the rewards if i need to w8 20 min before my games?

replies.body: Leaverbusters or low priority queues don't disqualify you from any [**ranked rewards**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk?sort_type=recent).
